            "body": "Thanks.\r\n\r\nI can verify that `globpath` is a workaround:\r\n```\r\n:set wildignorecase\r\n:echo glob(\"temp/test/*\", 0, 1)\r\n:echo globpath(\".\",\"temp/test/*\", 0, 1)\r\n```\r\nreturns\r\n```\r\n[]\r\n['./temp/test/test.txt']\r\n```\r\non NVIM v0.2.2\r\n\r\n\r\nLuckily, I'm no longer forced to use the computer with wonky permissions.",
